verbose_text: Above all, we tested the shelter effect of the liposome in delivering alphaGC via the iNKT cells reactivation assay, the IFN-gamma level of alphaGC-TH-Lip group remained high after the second injection, in contrast to the IFN-gamma production of free alphaGC group that was significantly reduced after the readminstration, which provided the basis for the further experiments.
